      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 1259: Edition entries are tagged with latestEditionId before replacing the body, but the pending-edition path in handleMessage() only sets latestEditionId to the newest pending edit and does not add equivalent ids to each superseded body in the editions list. That makes bodyOverwrite lookup for historical editions inconsistent depending on whether edits arrived before or after the parent message. Apply the same id-tagging logic when replaying pending editions.",
