      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 121: The new global services reloadBodyOverwriteConversations, clearSwarmBodyOverwrite, and bodyOverwriteLoadedConversations affect every account and every loaded conversation regardless of which plugin invoked them. A single plugin can clear or retrigger body overwrites produced by unrelated plugins across the daemon. Prefer the scoped conversation variants, or scope global operations to the invoking plugin\u0027s enabled conversations and plugin-owned keys rather than clearing all pluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"].",
